== 評價 ==
網站「Forbes.com」稱Firefox為「2004年最佳瀏覽器」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.forbes.com/2004/09/29/cx_ah_0929tentech.html | title=Better Browser Now The Best | last=Hesseldahl | first=Arik | publisher=''Forbes'' | date=2004-09-29 | accessdate=2006-10-17 | archive-date=2006-10-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061024132426/http://www.forbes.com/2004/09/29/cx_ah_0929tentech.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，雜誌《PC World》在「2005年最佳百大產品」中也將Firefox列入<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.techhive.com/article/120763/article.html | title = The 100 Best Products of 2005 | accessdate = 2007-01-24 | date = 2005-06-01 | author = ''PC World'' | archive-date = 2013-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130609075317/http://www.techhive.com/article/120763/article.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，在Firefox 2和Internet Explorer 7推出的2006年，PC World也對這兩個瀏覽器做出評論，並認為Firefox是比較好的瀏覽器<ref name="pcworldreview">{{cite web | url = http://www.pcworld.com/article/127309/article.html | title = Radically New IE 7 or Updated Mozilla Firefox 2--Which Browser Is Better? | accessdate = 2007-05-18 | last = Larkin | first = Erik | date = 2006-10-24 | archive-date = 2009-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090502044304/http://www.pcworld.com/article/127309/article.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。雜誌《Which?》也提名Firefox為最佳的網頁瀏覽器<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.which.co.uk/reports_and_campaigns/computers_and_internet/reports/internet/using_the_internet/Web%20browsers/pp_excel_546_114959.jsp |title=Mozilla Firefox 2 (PC) |accessdate=2007-07-09 |date=2006-10-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080310185407/http://www.which.co.uk/reports_and_campaigns/computers_and_internet/reports/internet/using_the_internet/Web%20browsers/pp_excel_546_114959.jsp |archivedate=2008-03-10 }}</ref>。英国Vnunet网站甚至把Firefox的市场份额的不断攀升列为10大鼓舞人心[[IT|IT]]事件之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vnunet.com/vnunet/news/2235412/top-inspiring-moments?page=4 |title=Top 10 most inspiring moments in IT |accessdate=2009-02-01 |archive-date=2009-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206085015/http://www.vnunet.com/vnunet/news/2235412/top-inspiring-moments?page=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

媒體《Internet Week》在一篇文章中提到許多讀者在使用Firefox 1.5時記憶體用量相當的高<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.informationweek.com/software/opensource/174909795 |title=Firefox 1.5: Not Ready For Prime Time? |accessdate=2007-01-24 |last=Finnie |first=Scot |date=2005-12-08 |publisher=InternetWeek |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090624202020/http://www.informationweek.com/news/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=174909795 |archivedate=2009-06-24 }}</ref>。Mozilla的開發團隊表示Firefox 1.5記憶體用量的升高是因為新的「上一頁／下一頁」（FastBack）功能所導致的<ref>{{cite web |last=Goodger |first=Ben |authorlink=Ben Goodger |title=About the Firefox 'memory leak' |work=MozllaZine weblogs |date=2006-02-14 |url=http://weblogs.mozillazine.org/ben/archives/009749.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717141231/http://weblogs.mozillazine.org/ben/archives/009749.html |archivedate=2011-07-17 |accessdate=2007-11-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外設計錯誤的擴充套件，像是某些舊版的[[Adblock|Adblock]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kb.mozillazine.org/index.php?title=Problematic_extensions&oldid=30448 | title = Problematic Extensions | accessdate = 2007-01-24 | author = MozillaZine Knowledge Base contributors | date = 2007-01-19 | publisher = MozillaZine Knowledge Base | archive-date = 2007-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930081243/http://kb.mozillazine.org/index.php?title=Problematic_extensions&oldid=30448 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，或者一些外掛程式（plug-ins）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kb.mozillazine.org/index.php?title=Adobe_Reader&oldid=30451 | title = Adobe Reader | accessdate = 2007-01-24 | author = MozillaZine Knowledge Base contributors | date = 2007-01-17 | publisher = MozillaZine Knowledge Base | archive-date = 2007-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930081746/http://kb.mozillazine.org/index.php?title=Adobe_Reader&oldid=30451 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 也是造成記憶體使用量增多的原因。《PC Magazine》比較了Firefox、[[Opera電腦瀏覽器|Opera]]、[[Internet_Explorer|Internet Explorer]]這三個瀏覽器的記憶體使用量，認為Firefox的記憶體使用量接近其他兩個瀏覽器<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,1991370,00.asp |title=Which New Browser Is Best: Firefox 2, Internet Explorer 7, or Opera 9? |accessdate=2007-01-24 |date=2006-07-19 |last=Muchmore |first=Michael W. |work=PC Magazine |archive-date=2008-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080317040651/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,1991370,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外由《PC World》和《Zimbra》的測試也指出Firefox 2的記憶體用量少於Internet Explorer 7<ref name="pcworldreview" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.zimbra.com/blog/archives/2006/10/ie_7_a_better_b.html | title = IE 7 vs IE 6 | accessdate = 2007-01-24 | date = 2006-10-19 | last = Dargahi | first = Ross | publisher = ''Zimbra'' | archive-date = 2007-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070125085230/http://www.zimbra.com/blog/archives/2006/10/ie_7_a_better_b.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，還在測試中的Firefox 3（以beta 1版本來進行測試）記憶體使用量沒有低於Firefox 2，不過仍然少於Internet Explorer 7<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kejut.com/browsermemory | title = Memory Usage Test: Firefox 2 & 3, Opera 9, IE 7 | accessdate = 2007-11-24 | archive-date = 2007-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071125140402/http://www.kejut.com/browsermemory | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

如同其他的瀏覽器一樣，Firefox也有一些安全漏洞，可能會影響使用者的電腦安全，不過根據CERT的統計，Firefox的安全漏洞也少於Internet Explorer<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.computerworld.com/article/2488477/microsoft-windows/us-cert-urges-xp-users-to-dump-ie.html | title =US-CERT urges XP users to dump IE | date =2014-05-11 | accessdate =2015-03-15 | archive-date =2015-04-08 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150408195511/http://www.computerworld.com/article/2488477/microsoft-windows/us-cert-urges-xp-users-to-dump-ie.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

《[[Softpedia|Softpedia]]》的測試指出Firefox比起其他瀏覽器需要比較長的啟動時間<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/windows/Mozilla-Firefox-Review-13677.shtml | title = Mozilla Firefox 1.5 Final Review | accessdate = 2007-01-24 | date = 2005-01-30 | last = Muradin | first = Alex | publisher = Softpedia | archive-date = 2006-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061027180757/http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/windows/Mozilla-Firefox-Review-13677.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，IE6也比Firefox有稍快的啟動速度，不過這是因為IE用到的程式組件有些在Windows啟動後就載入了，因此會有較快的啟動時間。

但也有评论家大唱反调：根據2009年一篇刊登在《PC World》杂志上的分析文章称，在与Chrome浏览器的竞争中，Firefox浏览器正逐渐失去電腦专家的青睐。尽管Mozilla基金会仍致力于一些宏大的目标，但火狐浏览器已经宣告死亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/161637/firefox_may_already_be_dead.html|title=Firefox May Already Be Dead|date=2009-03-20|accessdate=2013-07-25|archive-date=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410061905/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/161637/firefox_may_already_be_dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

